Bosse_Ramuh_Status_Fury's Bolt_Desc: Overcharged with electricity. Next attack will deal increased damage or differ in range.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Static Conde: Excess electricity is stored within your body, reducing HP recovery.
Bosse_Unknown Source_Status_Surge Protec: Your body is covered in conductive matter, reducing the damage of certain attacks.
ContentDesc_Edens Resonanz - Entladung: Although Gaia, the girl who had previously launched an attack on Eden, has finally awoken, her amnesia prevents you from learning much of her origins. For the time being, the best course of action appears to be continuing with efforts to restore balance to the ambient aether of the Empty. The next element is lightning, which once ravaged the Gandof Thunder Plains in the time before the Flood of Light. Your memories of Ramuh give corporeal form to the crackling aetherial energies drawn forth.
Instancecontenttextdata_24401_Text: Thou wouldst forge this world anew? I, Ramuh, shall test thy worth.
Instancecontenttextdata_24404_Text: From the storm of my judgment, thou shalt not escape!
Instancecontenttextdata_24405_Text: Swift as thou art, I am swifter still!
Instancecontenttextdata_24406_Text: The rolling of thunder foretells thy doom, mortal.
Instancecontenttextdata_24410_Text: 'Neath rolling cloud, unrelenting lightning doth strike!
Instancecontenttextdata_24413_Text: With all my might, I smite thee!
Instancecontenttextdata_24415_Text: O noble beasts of the levin, may none withstand your charge!
